00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,600
Here's what science actually says about adrenal stress response.

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:09,600
When we face stress, our body triggers the adrenal glands to release hormones like cortisol.

3
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:12,800
But what happens when this response is overactive?

4
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:16,800
It can lead to anxiety, fatigue, and even chronic illness.

5
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:20,400
Research shows that prolonged stress can alter DNA expression.

6
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:23,200
Yes, stress can actually change your genes!

7
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:28,400
Understanding this response helps us manage stress better and improve our overall health.

8
